== Use cases: ==

(a) // Checkout and build everything
$ aBuild git@github.com:DemoProject1.git # checksout and builds everything you need

(b) // Rebuild everything
$ cd DemoProjct1
$ aBuild <rebuild>

(c) // Update everything
$ cd DemoProject1
$ aBuild update

(d) // Test everything
$ cd DemoProject1
$ aBuild test

(e) // Create docu
$ cd DemoProject1
$ aBuild docu

== Progress ==
Progress:
